{"tid":1203912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家並不孤單... 台灣人一直在幫我們打氣","createTime":"2019-06-11T13:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T13:53:56.000Z","uid":38358,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"67b98fa06a88da311728540af0957da3c4e4a3f3","tid":1203912,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:45:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/PublicIssue/M.1560103490.A.FC1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FPublicIssue%2FM.1560103490.A.FC1.html&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=1fde2352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/PublicIssue/M.1560103490.A.FC1.html</a><br />\n台灣ptt 網<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4PABGfH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4PABGfH.jpg&h=ad727548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3mbupCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3mbupCd.jpg&h=0a842cfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v3AL3t5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv3AL3t5.jpg&h=af08bf74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uDDmt8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuDDmt8b.jpg&h=d95f7ec3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/n82hnwn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn82hnwn.jpg&h=0cb3fcd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/E6h4JgH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FE6h4JgH.jpg&h=0cad6b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;以下給香港人，粵語&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我唔係香港人，<br />\n唔過香港既文化同埋精神影響我至深<br />\n<br />\n因為哥哥<br />\n我了解每個人都有自己d色彩<br />\n<br />\n因為黃家駒，<br />\n我學會多d關心及貢獻比呢個社會同埋世界<br />\n<br />\n因為香港電影，<br />\n我d生活多左好多快樂同趣味<br />\n<br />\n因為香港音樂，我學左粵語。<br />\n<br />\n而家我仲係睇呢d電影、聽呢d音樂<br />\n我唔係香港人但我對香港係好有感情既。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日就係黃家駒既生日，<br />\n<br />\n佢講過：「你向這個社會需要一些東西的時候，第一個步驟你先問你自己給了些什麼給這<br />\n個社會。我給了音樂」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沙不怕風吹，在某天定會凝聚。</span></span></strong><br />\n而家，香港人獻出左自己比社會。<br />\n<br />\n粵語講得不係幾好啦，<br />\n我在呢度比大家少少d支持，係我唯一可以做d嘢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n祝福香港"},{"pid":"fced3c9e9fab11b886992bbebc745aad92d43bd1","tid":1203912,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5792e54c0857128685bd38946640d69b5f69bf25","tid":1203912,"uid":25750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"多謝您<br />\n<br />\n大家同仇敵愾 一起坑賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23649944566249bbfaac4ac6cd0b076a31eaf3ac","tid":1203912,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>支持台灣禁止所有警務人員入境</strong>"},{"pid":"68b91d257e662107466601cf6598a704d0d36a10","tid":1203912,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>支持台灣禁止所有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>警務人員入境</strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"afdc30c3f9ce0882069dafeb7b5b482f31f4f211","tid":1203912,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68b91d257e662107466601cf6598a704d0d36a10","tid":1203912,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong>支持台灣禁止所有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>警務人員入境</strong></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"台灣人可唔可以幫手"},{"pid":"21e2f27ff6b323784d3dc450b7464ce436a9cc50","tid":1203912,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T13:53:07.000Z","msg":"百萬散步仔💪"},{"pid":"56e9044ea9dda72e6510c5f73d11c8b92be79ac8","tid"